{"tid":1850690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會員逾15000人，逾3200醫護已經簽罷工宣言","createTime":"2020-01-29T16:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:07:40.000Z","uid":125168,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a03e6d1f0a9292581d8ea840c11da616ae5372e4","tid":1850690,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"醫管局員工陣線逾3200醫護簽罷工宣言<br />\n<br />\n有公立醫院醫護不滿政府未有全面封關，醞釀罷工。醫管局員工陣線表示，已有3200多名醫護簽署罷工宣言，未達到4000人的罷工最低門檻。已簽署罷工宣言的醫護，有7成人屬於緊急服務崗位。而以職系計算，有7成是護士，1成是專職醫療人員，不足1成是醫生。工會將於星期六召開會員大會，如果響應罷工的人數足夠而醫管局未能回應訴求，會在下星期一發動工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n2020-01-30 00:01:55"},{"pid":"7851a7239423e43ba6ebfddb4a618bec5d11736d","tid":1850690,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454973cb2170ca751b87ec30c183233fe5d8bd87","tid":1850690,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"點解會入左又唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185e51f7fdc946e8e56edfb49d1929722c542213","tid":1850690,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"77e6c725f04a1b0e94773c83ab9ca86d7d684606","tid":1850690,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"454973cb2170ca751b87ec30c183233fe5d8bd87","tid":1850690,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"點解會入左又唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"會冇左份工/使命感"},{"pid":"f86405b8d48b2e6972d6b5c1cf0a4ad45989